snippet.textDisplay:
The least amazing would have to be Twilight Princess.

-equips flame shield, raises flame defense by over nine THOUSAND points-

That's not to say it's a bad game, it was just the Zelda that didn't impress me as much as the others. Sure the Ganondorf fight was epic, but he was essentially a Dark Nut and that was a bad choice. He should've had a different fighting style, yadda yadda.

I do like the darker tone of TP,but other than that it wasn't as amazing as everybody said it was.
